{"tid":1865710,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"葉劉淑儀: 醫管局員工陣線罷工是要求政府全面封關，這根本與他們的行業無關，也干犯了「公職人員行為失當」罪","createTime":"2020-02-06T10:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T22:08:05.000Z","uid":167469,"like":7,"dislike":191,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"e1f130c7948e764dda453c6248fb91926a2db5f7","tid":1865710,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:32:06.000Z","msg":"【民間團體投訴罷工醫護人員行為失當】<br />\n<br />\n今日，有民間團體就「醫管局員工陣線」近日發起的罷工行動到廉政公署投訴，指參與罷工的醫護人員行為失當。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我認為員工陣線表示，罷工行動受基本法保障的說法，是對條例有所誤解及不恰當。該團體煽動其他醫管局人員擅離職守，反而干犯了公職人員行為不當的罪名。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根據職工會條例（香港法例332章）第一部的釋義部分指出：「罷工 (strike)......作為迫使他們的僱主、另一人或另一群人的僱主，或任何受僱的人或一群受僱的人，接受或不接受僱傭條款或條件或影響僱傭的條款或條件的方法；」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">換言之，罷工的原因須與員工的僱傭條款或工作條件有關；若今次罷工是為了爭取加薪、福利、改善工作環境、增加保護裝備等，尚可符合法例上罷工的要求。然而，員工陣線早已表示今次罷工是要求政府全面封關，這根本與他們的行業無關。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另外，法例同時列明罷工的對象須與員工有僱傭關係，但員工陣線要求的談判對象卻是特首而非醫管局。醫管局行政總裁高拔陞亦早已表明，有關要求屬醫管局權力範圍以外。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">由此可見，今次罷工並非工業行動，實際上乃政治事件，目的只是為了向政府施壓，而非為員工爭取權益，故此並不受法例保障。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根據廉政公署《公共機構僱員行為守則範本》第33條有關「公職人員行為失當」列明：「(c) 藉作為或不作為而故意作出不當行為，例如故意忽略或不履行其職責； 」及「(e) 考慮到有關公職和任職者的責任、他們所促進的公共目標的重要性及偏離責任的性質和程度，有關的失當行為屬於嚴重而非微不足道。」<br />\n<br />\n在現今疫情嚴峻的當下，參與罷工的醫護人員拒絕覆行自己的責任，可見的而且確干犯了「公職人員行為失當」的罪名，市民向廉政公署投訴，實是法理所在。<br />\n<br />\nsource: 葉劉淑儀facebook"},{"pid":"34af6b7da8b2b4c9c22e8ee63727728c4d275d4e","tid":1865710,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:34:19.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"ea59ec074aa3d29d80af6609aa78982d1d4e8393","tid":1865710,"uid":235152,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"拉人未講咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ed113db5b64e2f11be7e2e6950524e3328c2b8","tid":1865710,"uid":82938,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:34:59.000Z","msg":"無關？"},{"pid":"45139be0c6d7d2dbb5f137571e915cf3820be24d","tid":1865710,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba11759f4001dea22404752f3fdb95beb8e7125f","tid":1865710,"uid":104258,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"ea59ec074aa3d29d80af6609aa78982d1d4e8393","tid":1865710,"uid":235152,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"拉人未講咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:37:02.000Z","msg":"無gear慘過坐監"},{"pid":"141c68f9cc9cacd8557094b8a1f86584761d0750","tid":1865710,"uid":5191,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地淨係話全面封關<br />\n佢地都有講要增加裝備<br />\n咁係咪姐係合理<br />\n而你又自打嘴巴？"},{"pid":"208ad785598a5d9c8444e9db1b488e11011572c5","tid":1865710,"uid":85629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:38:53.000Z","msg":"同妹妹一樣<br />\n知道自己下場好慘所以發晦氣？"},{"pid":"56079ef242042f12d0aa7b4306d95df95953d9ae","tid":1865710,"uid":310700,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyKb2HL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyKb2HL.jpg&h=6eb0b3d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C8S84V6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC8S84V6.jpg&h=cfa23a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sK2AKV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsK2AKV7.jpg&h=9e3afc35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"772087951d0807a56e69605ac76e0bad8bc1456f","tid":1865710,"uid":128594,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:39:43.000Z","msg":"改善工作環境囉柒頭"},{"pid":"a8568d82f37ebe884ec1cce267f9119c63d437b8","tid":1865710,"uid":51411,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:40:50.000Z","msg":"Ha唔係政府工 都算係公職？<br />\n純好奇"},{"pid":"76c738607018b39cd23af2a07fc899687b5caffd","tid":1865710,"uid":113163,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:42:24.000Z","msg":"改善工作環境 &gt; 爭取封闗咪令工作環境變得安全<br />\n增加保護裝備&gt; 咪要確保防護裝備供應<br />\n<br />\n係咪太認真!?"},{"pid":"38f64fc23a4e536bbacaa3125d590562a9952f50","tid":1865710,"uid":64337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:44:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢認為</span></span> 佢係咩專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc410a4e872a6a9f3ccc54980a612ad436003f70","tid":1865710,"uid":73192,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a8568d82f37ebe884ec1cce267f9119c63d437b8","tid":1865710,"uid":51411,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:40:50.000Z","msg":"Ha唔係政府工 都算係公職？<br />\n純好奇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:45:24.000Z","msg":"唔算 佢係on9 可ignore"},{"pid":"b2f51f8edaffabab9d4c9afb9ece8108a7a28dd0","tid":1865710,"uid":164623,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e1f130c7948e764dda453c6248fb91926a2db5f7","tid":1865710,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:32:06.000Z","msg":"【民間團體投訴罷工醫護人員行為失當】<br />\n<br />\n今日，有民間團體就「醫管局員工陣線」近日發起的罷工行動到廉政公署投訴，指參與罷工的醫護人員行為失當。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我認為員工陣線表示，罷工行動受基本法保障的說法，是對條例有所誤解及不恰當。該團體煽動其他醫管局人員擅離職守，反而干犯了公職人員行為不當的罪名。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根據職工會條例（香港法例332章）第一部的釋義部分指出：「罷工 (strike)......作為迫使他們的僱主、另一人或另一群人的僱主，或任何受僱的人或一群受僱的人，接受或不接受僱傭條款或條件或影響僱傭的條款或條件的方法；」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">換言之，罷工的原因須與員工的僱傭條款或工作條件有關；若今次罷工是為了爭取加薪、福利、改善工作環境、增加保護裝備等，尚可符合法例上罷工的要求。然而，員工陣線早已表示今次罷工是要求政府全面封關，這根本與他們的行業無關。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另外，法例同時列明罷工的對象須與員工有僱傭關係，但員工陣線要求的談判對象卻是特首而非醫管局。醫管局行政總裁高拔陞亦早已表明，有關要求屬醫管局權力範圍以外。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">由此可見，今次罷工並非工業行動，實際上乃政治事件，目的只是為了向政府施壓，而非為員工爭取權益，故此並不受法例保障。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根據廉政公署《公共機構僱員行為守則範本》第33條有關「公職人員行為失當」列明：「(c) 藉作為或不作為而故意作出不當行為，例如故意忽略或不履行其職責； 」及「(e) 考慮到有關公職和任職者的責任、他們所促進的公共目標的重要性及偏離責任的性質和程度，有關的失當行為屬於嚴重而非微不足道。」<br />\n<br />\n在現今疫情嚴峻的當下，參與罷工的醫護人員拒絕覆行自己的責任，可見的而且確干犯了「公職人員行為失當」的罪名，市民向廉政公署投訴，實是法理所在。<br />\n<br />\nsource: 葉劉淑儀facebook"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:45:52.000Z","msg":"咁你告佢囉 <br />\n葉劉法庭見"},{"pid":"d2408c67abc820d574f4b787b1acadb9804deeb4","tid":1865710,"uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:47:02.000Z","msg":"變左公務員 ?"},{"pid":"54cb12922dac1b7198ee1d7cf43deca2ce7871b2","tid":1865710,"uid":167469,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"a8568d82f37ebe884ec1cce267f9119c63d437b8","tid":1865710,"uid":51411,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:40:50.000Z","msg":"Ha唔係政府工 都算係公職？<br />\n純好奇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:47:40.000Z","msg":"HKSAR v Wong Lin Kay FACC 3/2011：終審法院在本案釐清了「公職人員」的定義。香港漁農自然護理署所僱用的司機黃連基在因為觸犯酒後駕駛罪而被停牌期間沒有向署方報告，照常駕駛公務車輛進出郊野公園，原被裁定公職人員行為失當罪成，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但高等法院及終審法院均認為政府公務車司機的身份並無行政權力，因此被告不算普通法下的「公職人員」，改判罪名不成立。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/公職人員行為失當\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%85%AC%E8%81%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA%E5%A4%B1%E7%95%B6&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAspgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=7817f23a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/公職人員行為失當</a>"},{"pid":"a6a702064e22c4989a12713c1a605bf7ba68fb23","tid":1865710,"uid":18113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc410a4e872a6a9f3ccc54980a612ad436003f70","tid":1865710,"uid":73192,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a8568d82f37ebe884ec1cce267f9119c63