-02-06T11:00:35.000Z","msg":"架係自己攞嚟丟"},{"pid":"32eeacd118a957a53a03a8bba651d641b7cbba3e","tid":1865710,"uid":116683,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c0ed113db5b64e2f11be7e2e6950524e3328c2b8","tid":1865710,"uid":82938,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:34:59.000Z","msg":"無關？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"關醫護事，關病人事，關香港事，就係唔關葉劉事。<br />\n<br />\n呢度無葉劉嘅事，麻煩佢收爹。<br />\n<br />\n大爆發都半個月，政府都未準備好封關，明顯係唔踢佢就唔郁。<br />\n<br />\n成件事根本最有say係醫護，唔滿意嘅自己去一轉武漢醫院觀察下先再講野，不過去左唔好番黎累人類物啦。"},{"pid":"a3e749585e7c191c004e6dfae77eb28a36a6f274","tid":1865710,"uid":97398,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"effa90cac7677f1de80873a8e78e93df1fb4b479","tid":1865710,"uid":169869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:53:37.000Z","msg":"係？<br />\n炒曬啲人未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:01:39.000Z","msg":"拉晒醫護去坐監囉，等警犬去醫人"},{"pid":"fcf6028594571fc1ee0e92af903d38459dbcdd95","tid":1865710,"uid":325981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:02:03.000Z","msg":"我好驚呀, 炒左人未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b44c87770681c302ba5626f728548c2cf6b281f","tid":1865710,"uid":18185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:02:08.000Z","msg":"咁要求有足夠防護裝備咪係待遇囉<br />\n屌戇鳩鳩"},{"pid":"e684abd02d4b5ee5ef8fc4c0c7a31a3f9407a233","tid":1865710,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:03:47.000Z","msg":"大量病人入港播毒<br />\n加重香港醫療負擔<br />\n<br />\n沙士果時感染左幾百個醫護人士唔通係假架？<br />\n<br />\n點解唔關醫護事？<br />\n<br />\n遲下到葉劉有肺炎"},{"pid":"29eeafaa3c959fd4879e93d3596f537506eb1071","tid":1865710,"uid":115042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:07:13.000Z","msg":"佢其實係咪又想補多兩刀插死柒婆？<br />\n上次反送中已經係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2cc20e19c9b24a0abb554b49608213b757dcb22","tid":1865710,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0